    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "[REDACTED], Kokomo,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "Indiana, on July 30, 1952, advised that on July 27, 1952,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "at approximately 10:00 A. M. while fishing in the back",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "waters of Thessalon Lake, Ontario, Canada, he noticed a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "formation of bombing planes, sixteen to twenty in number,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "in two groups flying south at a height estimated by him to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "be four or five miles.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "Dr. [REDACTED] stated that the planes went over the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "lake and suddenly dropped objects, at first thought by him",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "to be parachutes. He continued that these objects fell",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "straight for a short time, then suddenly spurted vapor",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "and at a high rate of speed flew off in a southwesterly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "direction.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "Dr. [REDACTED] was unable to identify the nationality",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
